                    <span>This is a good movie but not great. It's way too long and the actors are not really that good. The special effects are amazing to look at but it gets boring after a while. Jennifer Garner had a very small role in the movie. Why didn't she got a bigger part is beyond me. This unrated version is not that special only has a lot more gore/violence. Why did I waste time and money on this one I really don't know. If you love violence movies buy this now if now avoid it at all costs.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Pearl Harbore, and inaccurate</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
